metadata.name: Chunk Remix
metadata.description:
This piece is titled 'Chunk Remix', based off one of my (lolwtferic) characters. I wanted to make a messy, striking stream of consciousness, psychedelic pop art. 

I allowed myself to be in a bit of trance while listening to music and it's rhythms to guide each brush stroke. 

Erratic, yet cohesive as the goal.
